    "source": [
     "## Yield and ROI Calculation\n",
     "\n",
     "In betting analysis, we distinguish between two key metrics:\n",
     "- **Yield**: Efficiency of betting (Profit / Total Staked). This is the most important metric for evaluating a model's edge.\n",
     "- **ROI**: Return on initial capital (Profit / Initial Bankroll).\n",
     "\n",
     "### Yield Formula\n",
     "$$\\text{Yield} = \\frac{\\sum \\text{Profit}}{\\sum \\text{Stake}} \\times 100\\%$$\n",
     "\n",
     "### Bookmaker Performance Analysis\n",
     "\n",
     "We have implemented a script `scripts/17_bookmaker_performance.py` that evaluates the metamodel's performance across different bookmakers individually. Below is the summary of results for the period 2024-2026 (including 12% tax and 1% slippage):"
    ]
   },
